This commit transforms the setClassMetadata calls generated by ngtsc from:

```typescript
/*@__PURE__*/ setClassMetadata(...);
```

to:

```typescript
/*@__PURE__*/ (function() {
  setClassMetadata(...);
})();
```

This is required for the build optimizer and side-effect-free analysis to
function correctly.

